{"article_id":"BCjSwvigW6x8PVBd","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US President Donald Trump has said","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"there is a `` very substantial chance ''","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"a historic summit with North Korea 's Kim Jong-un next month may not happen .","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"the North must meet conditions","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"for the summit to go ahead","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"though","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"if it did not ,","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"it might happen `` later '' .","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"Mr Trump was speaking","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"as he received South Korea 's President Moon Jae-in at the White House .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"The North has said","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"it may cancel the summit","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"if the US insists on it giving up nuclear weapons unilaterally .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Mr Trump did not say","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"what conditions the US had set for the summit","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"but ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"asked by a reporter about the North 's arsenal ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"`` denuclearisation must take place '' .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"The 12 June summit is due to take place in Singapore .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"It follows a historic meeting between the two Korean leaders in April .","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"Meanwhile , North Korea has agreed to let in journalists from the South","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"to watch the dismantling of its nuclear test site .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"The group ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"who had earlier been denied visas ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"will join a team of international media","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"who are in the country","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"to visit Punggye-ri over the next few days .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"The demolition of the site has been billed as a goodwill gesture","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"but may be delayed by bad weather .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"`` There are certain conditions","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that we want","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and I think","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"we 'll get those conditions","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"and if we do n't","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"we do n't have the meeting .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"`` You go into deals","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"that are 100 % certain -","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"it does n't happen .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"You go into deals","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"that have no chance","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"and it happens","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"and , sometimes , happens easily . ''","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"He also said","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Kim Jong-un 's attitude had changed after his second visit to China , earlier this month .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Later in the day , during a news conference , Secretary of State Mike Pompeo adopted a more positive position ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"the US was still working towards the 12 June date .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"He commended China","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"for offering `` historic assistance ''","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"in putting pressure on North Korea .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"The optimistic build-up to the summit gave way to a reality check","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"that was bound to happen sooner or later .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"With Kim Jong-un tapping the brakes","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"and refusing to accept `` unilateral demands '' to disarm ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"President Trump also took a step back .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"He set his own conditions ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"although he did n't say","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"what they were .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"He did stress","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"that it would be worth it for the North Korean leader to risk denuclearisation ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"throwing the ball back into Mr Kim 's court .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"The build-up to the summit has been shaped by an unusual degree of public showmanship by both leaders , a diplomatic version of their hostile exchanges last year .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"while the threats and insults worked at the rhetorical level ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"this is about substantive issues","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"where the detail matters .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"President Moon Jae-in also has his spin .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"He really wants to seize this opportunity for South Korea 's sake","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"and continues to be determined in his optimism ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"leaving some here wondering","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"whether he 's been overstating Kim Jong-un 's willingness to deal .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"North Korea cancelled high-level talks with South Korea ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"the South 's joint military exercises with the US","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"- which it had previously said","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"it would tolerate -","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"were a `` provocation '' .","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"Pyongyang then accused US national security adviser John Bolton of making `` reckless statements '' for his suggestion","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"that the North could follow a `` Libya model '' of denuclearisation .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"That was a reference to Libya 's former leader , Muammar Gaddafi ,","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"who agreed to give up nuclear weapons in 2003","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"and was later killed by Western-backed rebels .","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"Mr Trump later denied","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"the US would follow the `` Libyan model ''","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"if an agreement was reached with North Korea .","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"`` That model would take place","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"if we do n't make a deal , most likely .","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"But","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"if we make a deal ,","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"I think","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"Kim Jong-un is going to be very , very happy . ''","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"Please upgrade your browser","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"to view this content .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"Timeline hide","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"How Trump and Kim have changed their tone","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"What happened next ?","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"Show all","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"Was this timeline useful ?","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Yes No","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"Thank you for your feedback .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Share this timeline","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"It would be historic","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"as no sitting US president has ever met a North Korean leader .","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"Mr Trump accepted North Korea 's invitation for direct talks after more than a year of heated rhetoric and with global concern","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"that hostilities might escalate into military confrontation .","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"The New York Times reported on Sunday","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"that Mr Trump was asking aides and advisers","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"whether the meeting should go ahead .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"North Korea conducted several nuclear tests over the past few years","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"and developed long-distance missiles","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"which ,","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"it says ,","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"can carry nuclear bombs as far as the US mainland .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"Many observers had argued","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"before Mr Trump met Mr Moon","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"that there was too much at stake for Washington and Pyongyang not to proceed with the Singapore summit .","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"However , Pyongyang 's professed commitment to `` denuclearisation '' is likely to differ from Washington 's demand for `` comprehensive , verifiable and irreversible '' nuclear disarmament .","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"A group of Western , Russian and Chinese journalists have been invited by the North to its remote Punggye-ri nuclear test site ahead of its demolition .","depth":4},{"id":120,"text":"They were flown into the North Korean port city of Wonsan","depth":5},{"id":121,"text":"but their onward journey was postponed by bad weather ,","depth":5},{"id":122,"text":"Tom Cheshire from the UK 's Sky News tweets .","depth":3},{"id":123,"text":"The site , in the mountainous north-east , is thought to be the North 's main nuclear facility and the only active nuclear testing site in the world .","depth":3},{"id":124,"text":"Testing has taken place in a system of tunnels","depth":4},{"id":125,"text":"dug below nearby Mount Mantap .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":251,"left":244,"right":250,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":244,"left":228,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":147,"right":227,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":145,"right":146,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":139,"right":144,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":139,"left":136,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":134,"right":135,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":128,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":0,"right":127,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":3,"right":132,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":132,"left":129,"right":131,"relation":"a